{"tid":1106081,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"(輪緊公屋請入)入息問題","createTime":"2019-04-14T10:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T23:17:47.000Z","uid":205134,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad413789898497b28b786c6646e9403e22a30cf","tid":1106081,"uid":205134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"我家陣單人輪咗5年左右<br />\n黎緊仲有兩年讀完書<br />\n預計出到黎會揾20-25K<br />\n<br />\n想問下如果我返工途中配到公屋<br />\n我即刻遲工再簽租約<br />\n係咪就唔算超過入息限額？<br />\n定係佢個入息限額係平均一年咁計？<br />\n<br />\n利申：無父母幹，草根只求有瓦遮頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582b9cee56a6d8eb47e0139e178e8d587e66c5d0","tid":1106081,"uid":185647,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知單人平均輪候時間要幾耐⋯除非你往後十幾年都唔過入息，否則你唔會輪到。"},{"pid":"756b3c641de6e0235a6e475f47390d9004650135","tid":1106081,"uid":205134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582b9cee56a6d8eb47e0139e178e8d587e66c5d0","tid":1106081,"uid":185647,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知單人平均輪候時間要幾耐⋯除非你往後十幾年都唔過入息，否則你唔會輪到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"如果接果時唔超得唔得<br />\n講真我都係搏入左之後超入息比雙租三租<br />\n我估佢都唔會咁快review再查有無超"},{"pid":"6748bd8d79c4fdf989c3198939cdceba0c77b60a","tid":1106081,"uid":170133,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"讀咩可以一grad就$20k up?"},{"pid":"991d7d2fac11c1f926adb6ffad1879965e8655f2","tid":1106081,"uid":103248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"Check過往一年"},{"pid":"428fe39f612c46cffe2489c6a569ed89b65792bd","tid":1106081,"uid":103248,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"同埋單身要排30年..所以唔好FF太多"},{"pid":"ce7dc1ee0a6c337630af6ca302717105241ab277","tid":1106081,"uid":86186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"排左先5年就算吧啦<br />\n